<% title("Hymns") %>

	<p><span class="cap">T</span>hese hymns with the exceptions of
	those from the Bristol and Skyland Conference, were recorded
	in the year 1957 for use on the Gospel Center's radio
	broadcast known as <i>Sunday Night Meditations</i>. The Gospel
	Center was one of two New Testament assemblies in Durham,
	N.C. at that time. These of course are not the latest digital
	stereo but are good quality mono. All are thought to be in the
	public domain. If any are possibly found to not be public
	domain, they will be promptly removed. If you feel that you
	are the copyright or royalty owner for any of these, please
	email info@voicesforChrist.org and we will address your
	concerns.</p> <hr />
      </div>

